{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_09_02",
  "title": "白石千紗 2話 一緒に感じてほしいんです",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うーん……このデザインにするには\nお金が掛かり過ぎちゃうし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm… this design\nwould cost too much…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "アイデアが多過ぎてうまくまとまらないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "There are too many ideas and I can't organize them well…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.6666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.0666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "どうしよう……{user}さんが\nせっかく私に任せてくれたのに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What should I do… {user}-san\nwent to the trouble of entrusting this to me…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 18.5000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.1000000954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ここにいたのか\n衣装の検討は……順調ではなさそうだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were here.\nLooks like… the costume planning isn't going so well.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.9021968842,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.0333334287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "すみません……デザインが沢山浮かび過ぎて\n一つに絞れなくって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm sorry… too many designs came to mind\nand I can't narrow it down to one…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.7000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "行き詰まってしまっているようだし\n一旦落ち着いて考えてみるのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You seem to be stuck.\nHow about calming down and thinking it through?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.8666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 38.6666667621
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "例えば、そうだな……千紗が今回の衣装に\nどんな想いを込めたいのかとかさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "For example‚ let's see… what kind of feelings\ndo you want to put into this costume?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2666667621,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.8333334287
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "今回の衣装……確かに、みんなの意見を\nどう取り入れればいいかばかり考えちゃってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This costume… it's true that I was only thinking about\nhow to incorporate everyone's opinions.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "ライブにマッチした衣装のデザインを\n考えなくちゃいけませんよね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I need to think about costume designs\nthat match the live performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.7333321572,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 59.4333341917
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "星見市のイメージを取り入れたデザイン……\nうーん、何を入れたらいいんだろう……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A design that incorporates the image of Hoshimi City…\nHmm‚ what should I include…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8000008584,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "千紗の、今回のライブにかける想いを\nデザインに生かしてみるのはどうだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "How about incorporating your feelings\nabout this live into the design?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.3666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "想い、ですか？　私の想い……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Feelings? My feelings…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.9666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 72.9666695596
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.4000028929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと久々に共演出来るって思うと\n凄く嬉しい気持ちになります",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I think about performing lives with my sister after so long‚\nI feel really happy.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.2667693606,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "それに、私達念願の里帰りライブですから\n頑張らないとって思ってて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Plus‚ this is our long-awaited homecoming live\nso I think I have to work hard…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.6000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "うまく言葉に出来ないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Can't put it into words well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.4666695596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "はい……いろんなことを考えちゃって\n全然まとまらないです……すみません",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… I'm thinking about so many things\nand I can't organize them at all… sorry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "そうか。なら、ちょっと出かけようか\n気分転換でもして頭を少し整理しよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see. Then let's go out for a bit.\nLet's refresh and organize your thoughts a little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.9000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――星見市",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hoshimi City",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.3000028929,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1200.0000000000027,
          "startTime": 113.5000028929
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_coast-00-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_coast-00-000-evening",
      "startTime": 113.3666695596
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "海が夕日に照らされて綺麗ですね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The ocean looks beautiful illuminated by the sunset…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3000028929,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 33333.330440399994,
          "startTime": 147.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 67399.99710709999,
          "startTime": 181.7
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 102333.3304404,
          "startTime": 216.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
          "delay": 136566.66377380004,
          "startTime": 250.8666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "海沿いのランニングコースも懐かしいです\nみんなで毎日のようにここで走ってたなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The running course along the coast is nostalgic too.\nWe used to run here together almost every day~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0646514258,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "私は走るの苦手だからいつも周回遅れだったんですけど\nお姉ちゃんは私のことをずっと待っていてくれたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I was bad at running so I was always a lap behind\nbut my sister always waited for me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.8333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことがあったんだな……\n千紗も沙季も、本当にここからよく頑張ったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So that's what happened…\nBoth you and Saki really worked hard from here.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんがいたから頑張れたんです……そういえば\n小さい頃に水族館で迷子になったことがあるんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I could work hard because my sister was there… Come to think of it‚\nwhen I was little‚ we got lost at the aquarium.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.9333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs016.m4a",
      "text": "二人でお母さんを探し回って、でも見つからなくて\n私はつい泣いちゃって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We searched everywhere for our mother‚ but couldn't find her\nand I ended up crying…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 158.9000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs017.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん、泣き止まない私に何をしたと思います？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What do you think my sister did when I wouldn't stop crying?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.6666573526,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "うーん、沙季ならどうするかな……\n励ましの言葉を掛けたとか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ what would Saki do…\nMaybe she said encouraging words?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 171.4000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs018.m4a",
      "text": "イルカショーにまで連れて行って\n自分が水を掛けられる姿を見せてきたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She took me all the way to the dolphin show\nand showed me herself getting splashed with water.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 176.5666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs019.m4a",
      "text": "びしょ濡れになったお姉ちゃんを見て\n私、つい笑っちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seeing my sister soaking wet\nI couldn't help but laugh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 183.0000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs020.m4a",
      "text": "後から聞いたんですけどどれだけ慰めても泣き止まない\n私のために、意を決して水を被ったらしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard later that no matter what she did‚ I wouldn’t stop crying…\nso for my sake‚ she made up her mind to get splashed.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 190.4310141485,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs021.m4a",
      "text": "あれで笑ってくれなかったらもう水槽に飛び込むしか\nなかった、ってお姉ちゃん言ってました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that didn't make me laugh‚ she said the only thing left\nwas to jump into the tank.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 198.7666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "なるほどなぁ……沙季の妹想いなところは\n昔からだったんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Saki's caring toward her sister\nsince she was little.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 206.0000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs022.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ、そうなんです。この海を見ていると\nいろんなことを思い出すなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu‚ that's right. Looking at this ocean\nbrings back so many memories…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 212.7333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs023.m4a",
      "text": "……そうだ。私思いつきました\nこの星見の海を衣装のモチーフにしたいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's it. I have an idea.\nI want to use Hoshimi's ocean as the motif for the costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 220.9000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs024.m4a",
      "text": "月ストとサニピは海の綺麗な星見市でスタートして\nいろんな経験を積んできました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace started in beautiful seaside Hoshimi City\nand have gained various experiences.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 229.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs025.m4a",
      "text": "みんなにも、衣装を通じて私達の経験を\n一緒に感じてほしいんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to share our experiences with everyone\nthrough the costumes.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 236.5333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、ここに来るといろんなことを思い出すな\n……うん。俺もそのアイデアに賛成だよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Right‚ coming here brings back many memories.\n…Yeah. I agree with that idea too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 243.9000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs026.m4a",
      "text": "私達とファンのみんながいつまでもお互いのことを\n忘れない、そんな衣装が作れる気がします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I feel like I can create costumes where we and\nall our fans will never forget each other.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 251.537819288,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs027.m4a",
      "text": "……なんだかインスピレーションがわいてきました！\n私、すぐに戻ってデザインを考えてみますね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I'm feeling inspired!\nI'll go back right away and work on the design!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 259.2000028929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Several days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 264.1999906859,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.3000028929
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 265.3000028929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs028.m4a",
      "text": "デザイナーさん、見つかって良かったですね\nそれに、私のデザインも褒めてもらえて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm glad we found a designer.\nAnd they even complimented my design…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 269.9806403479,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 274.266626835
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs029.m4a",
      "text": "自分の作ったデザインがプロの方に褒められるなんて\n凄く嬉しいです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It makes me so happy to have my design praised\nby a professional.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 279.4333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "それだけ千紗のデザインを気に入ってくれたんだよ\n千紗が頑張ったおかげだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They liked your design that much‚ Chisa\nIt's because you worked so hard.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 284.7489462536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 287.0332935017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs030.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ……予算の相談と生地の発注も\n済んでいますから、後は完成を待つだけですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe… the budget consultation and fabric orders\nare also done‚ so now we just wait for completion.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 291.0666695596,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "成長したなぁ、千紗は\n俺が手伝わなくても全部一人で出来るなんて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You've grown so much‚ Chisa.\nTo be able to do everything by yourself without my help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 298.6333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs031.m4a",
      "text": "ふふっ。なんだかお父さんみたいですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fufu. You sound like a father.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 301.9332935017,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 301.9332935017
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designoffice-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designoffice-00-noon",
      "startTime": 305.7332935017
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs032.m4a",
      "text": "衣装が完成するのが楽しみですね\nそれまでにレッスンも頑張らなくっちゃ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm looking forward to the costumes being completed.\nI have to work hard on lessons until then.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 309.1333362263,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_09_02-chs033.m4a",
      "text": "せっかくお姉ちゃんと共演するんだから\nいいライブに出来るように頑張ります！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since I’ll be performing with my sister‚\nI'll work hard to make it a good live performance!",
        "id": ""
      },
